// | SHIFT |  F1 |  F2 |  F3 |  F4 |  F5 | --- | --- |  | --- | --- |  F6 |  F7 | F8  |  F9 |  F10 | F11  |
//                     | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |  | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
